    "Most notably, risk can be decomposed into its different components -usually, hazard, exposure, and vulnerability.",
    "As we will see in a moment, this approach, fairly common in risk analysis, allows to open different areas of intervention for mitigation.",
    "Since we aim to provide an analysis of AI-related risk that can fruitfully serve also as a ground for policy making, the multi-component analysis is the one adopted in this article.",
